      • isOverlappingAppointment

        public boolean isOverlappingAppointment​(Appointment appointment)
        Check for overlapping appointments Public for JavaDocs I use a Lambda here to easily accomplish several tasks to check if an appointment overlaps with any existing appointment. First it filters out out the appointment that is passed into the function. Then it loops through each appointment to see if the times overlap.
